page.title: 09OUR DENTAL UNIT
page.content: A working day for Mrs.Mulraney is very busy.She starts work at nine o'clock when the first person comes in. Mrs. Mulraney is the helper to the other lady,who is the dentist. Lots of things are involved in Mrs.Mulraney's job.There are about eighteen patients a day.There are a lot more things involved like the chair that goes up,down left,right the spitoon which is a basin beside the chair which has a flow of water and also they have a drill unit.One of the drills is powerful and one not so powerful,and also there is an Xray unit and light. The dental unit covers twenty three schools +pre school children, pregnant mothers,handecapped children/adults. She covers North Kyme to Partney to Tattershall to New York.They hope to become fully mobile in the future but the present surgery will stay here.
